quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  11,61,"I Tamud, gmat sen ÛüÜaliê, inna: \"a yagdud iw! Âabdet Öebbi! Ur tesâim ôebbi, war Neppa. Neppa Ixelq ikwen seg wakal, Izzde$ ikwen fellas. Ssutret aS ssmaê, sinna, steôoâet aS. Mass iw, s tidep, Iqeôb ed, Ippara d awal"
  11,62,"Nnan as: \"a Üaliê, ni$ telliv garane$, uqbel aya, d asirem nne$. Day ad a$ tekksev aâbad n wayen âabden imezwura nne$? Nekwni, s tidep, aql a$ di ccekk imcebbwel, $ef wayen u$uô la $ tneccdev"
  11,63,"Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Acu twalam ma ddi$ d ubeggen n Mass iw? Ifka yi d aêunu s$uôeS. Acu ara yi isellken seg ufus n Öebbi, ma aâûa$ $uôeS? Iyi ternam, siwa taxessaôt"
  11,64,"A yagdud iw! Tagi d tal$wemt n Öebbi, d assekni i kunwi. Eooet ep a ppeks di tmurt n Öebbi. Ur p pjeyyifet, mulac a kwen id isami uâaqeb iqeôben"
  11,65,"Gezmen as ivaôen. Inna: \"zhut deg ixxamen nnwen, krav wussan. Apan lemâahda ur nepwankaô"
  11,66,"Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nsellek Üaliê akked wid iumnen yides, s uêunu s$uône£, si ddell n wass nni. Ih, Mass ik d Uohid, d Uzmir"
  11,67,"Asu$u iwwet wid idensen, gwran d d imeslax deg ixxamen nnsen"
  11,68,"amzun ur rbiêen degsen. Day, s tidep, ur jhilen ara Tamud, ar Mass nnsen? Day maççi: \"akin Tamud"
  11,69,"Ni$ usan d imceggâen nne£ ar Ibôahim, s ubecceô. Nnan: \"tifrat\"! Inna: \"tifrat\"! Ur iâaîîel ara ibbwi d aâjmi icwin"
  11,70,"Mi iwala ifassen nnsen ur d ééilen ara $uôes, isêassef iten, iugad iten. Nnan: \"ur ppagwad, nekwni neppuceggaâ ed ar ugdud n Luî"
  11,71,"Tameîîut is tbedd, tevûa. Nbecceô ip s Isêaq, akked Yaâqub, deffir Isêaq"
  11,72,"Tenna: \"a lêif iw, day a d arwe$, nek d tam$aôt, u argaz agi inu, wesser? Ayagi, s tidep, d lwehma"
  11,73,"Nnan: \"day twehmev di lameô n Öebbi? Aêunu n Öebbi, akked lbaôaka S, fellawen ay at uxxam. Ih, Neppa d Amaâzuz, Mucaâ"
  11,74,"Mi s tekkes tugwdi i Ibôahim, u iusa t id ubecceô, inumer a£ $ef ugdud n Luî"
  11,75,"Ibôahim, s tidep, iêellem, ippanez, isteôoiâ"
  11,76,"A Ibôahim, ur keççem deg waya. Ni$ iusa d lameô n Mass ik. Nitni, a ten id ias uâaqeb, war tifrat"
  11,77,"Mi usan imceggâen nne£ ar Luî, innu$ben, ur isâi i$il a ten ifukk. Inna: \"wagi d ass uwâiô"
  11,78,"Iusa d ugdud is, zeêfen d $uôes. Llan, zik, xeddmen tucmitin. Inna: \"a yagdud iw! Atent an issi, nitenti zeddigit, i kunwi. Ëezbet i Öebbi, ur iyi pêeccimet ar inebgawen iw. Day ur illi ara, garawen, urgaz aêesbi"
  11,79,"Nnan: \"ni$ teéôiv ur nesâi lêeqq deg issi k. Keçç, s tidep, teéôiv d acu neb$a"
  11,80,"Inna: \"a lemmer i wen zmire$, ne$ sâi$ tayep ioehden"
  11,81,"Nnan: \"a Luî, nekwni d imceggâen n Mass ik. Ur k id ppawven. Öuê akked twacult ik, deg iv. Yiwen degwen ur d itezzi! Kkes ed tameîîut ik. Neppat, s tidep, a ppepwwet s wayen ara ten iwwten. Ih, ppaâud nnsen, taûebêit. Ni$ tqeôb ed tûebêit"
  11,82,"Mi d iusa lameô nne£, Nesredm ip. Nesse$li d fellas abruri n yiéôa ibelbaven n talaxt"
  11,83,"Pwanesxen ar Mass ik. Nitni, ur bâiden i imednas"